@node "It need" "What does MakeStereoPic need"

 It needs only ReqTools.library in your LIBS: and some bytes of free memory.
@endnode

@node "3D" "How to get into 3D"

   How to get into the 3rd dimension? There are some ways:

    1) Look at the reflexion of your face in the monitor. Now you see
       the picture blurly. That`s what we need. Watch the reflexion.
       It can take minutes before you feel that somethinq is
       happening. In a moment you can see 3 dimension.

    2) Look over the picture. The pictur gets blur. After some time
       your eyes begin to adapt to new situation and you will see 3D
       picture.
@endnode

