@node "Introduction" "Introduction"

   This program generates stereo-pictures from normal IFF/ILBM pictures.
This version is only available to generate the picture from the LoRes(16
colors picture). The lowest color in IFF picture is the deepest level in the
generated picture. (There could be some examplas for better understanding.)

   This program is FreeWare. You can copy it as long as You want. It can
become a part of public colection-disks.
                (I would like to be informed about it)
@endnode

@node "Usage" "Usage"

 It is very simple to use this program.

 You choose a IFF/ILBM (16 colors) picture by FileRequestr.
 Then the program generates the StereoPicture and shows it.
 After you press the Left Mouse Buton then you can Save the generated
picture if you like it.

 Quiting the program: just choose CANCEL in FileRequestr.
@endnode

